articles.author: Developer DAO (🧱, 🚀)
articles.description:
Do you use .cursorrules anon?

Kevin ⨀: If you're using Cursor, you absolutely have to use .cursorrules.
As a designer & frontend developer, my biggest fear is using AI to implement features that I don't fully understand— features that might add easily avoidable tech debt.
This is why I have Cursor automatically
